Number Guessing Game
Welcome to the Number Guessing Game! This is a simple Java console-based game where the computer picks a random number between 1 and 100, and you try to guess it.

How to Play
Guessing the Number: Enter your guess when prompted. The game will tell you if your guess is too high, too low, or correct.
Winning the Game: Keep guessing until you correctly guess the number, or until you run out of attempts.
Play Again: After each game, you'll have the option to play again.
Features
Randomly generated number between 1 and 100 for each game.
Option to play multiple games in succession.
Informative feedback on each guess (too high, too low, or correct).
Limited number of attempts per game.
Contributing
Contributions are welcome! If you have any suggestions, improvements, or bug fixes, feel free to open an issue or create a pull request.
